---
title: Creamy Bacon & Cannellini Bean Filo Pie  with Roast Veggies
description: This easy-to-make veggie deluxe pie is a taste sensation. Seasoned cannellini beans and veggies in a pie is already a great dinner, but bake the pie with a blanket of crispy filo to create the top and dinner just became a lot more exciting!

